name: Not A News Channel
summary: Listen to this episode from Rizamblings on Spotify. A deep dive into Project Function with special guest and fellow Co-Founder, Daryl Cecile. We ramble on orange juice, my issues with saying the word "water", and loads more on our Project Function journey (including a very exciting #PFAnnouncement!)  Finally, for the first time, we have an ominous 3rd voice who goes by the name of Mary.  Find our guests:  Project Function -> @PFNotts  Daryl Cecile -> @darylcecile  Maryanne Parkinson -> @BoxOfQwert  Don't forget to #RizambleAlong on Twitter, find me -> @rizbizkits
